    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/a0925ce50eddd0ce5dfb136c79c1fbe4.poster.avif?t=1724771761\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/a0925ce50eddd0ce5dfb136c79c1fbe4.webm?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/a0925ce50eddd0ce5dfb136c79c1fbe4.mp4?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>欢迎，探险家。你准备好再次进入长夜了吗？</strong>  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/5862274f7bf622e3e2cf624b546904db.poster.avif?t=1724771761\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/5862274f7bf622e3e2cf624b546904db.webm?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/5862274f7bf622e3e2cf624b546904db.mp4?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>&quot;这是一个迷人的双摇杆动作roguelike冒险游戏，强力渲染混乱的战斗、可爱的人物角色和神秘感！<br><br>  在探索‘黑暗山’——一个充满怪物、秘密和可爱角色的地下世界时，玩家将在三个随机生成的区域中进行解谜、升级和战斗，以躲避致命的风暴，并逃离到外面的世界。在这个被困在无尽时间循环中的古老半神和探险家王国中，揭开一连串的神秘面纱。<br><br>  ‘彼岸世界里’有什么宝藏在等着你？是否有办法阻止风暴的蔓延？你能逃脱无尽的时间循环吗？一切都可能在长夜之后揭晓。 <br> <br> <strong>释放混乱</strong> - 射击、躲避、投掷物品和使用超能力，在黑暗山中战斗。获得、叠加和组合强大的升级，对你的敌人造成毁灭性的破坏！&quot;  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/7e22cbfef2a582d99d44208b5f39ab8a.poster.avif?t=1724771761\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/7e22cbfef2a582d99d44208b5f39ab8a.webm?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/7e22cbfef2a582d99d44208b5f39ab8a.mp4?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>与山中居民交友</strong> - 在地下探险的旅程中，结识一群充满色彩的友好洞穴居民。完成支线任务，跟随他们的故事穿越多次冒险。  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/fdedaca93c5fe28a954712a9748ba814.poster.avif?t=1724771761\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/fdedaca93c5fe28a954712a9748ba814.webm?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/fdedaca93c5fe28a954712a9748ba814.mp4?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>在致命风暴中生存并发现山中的秘密</strong> - 在山中逃脱一股神秘的腐蚀力量的追击。平衡你的升级和时间，否则就要承担后果！每次游戏都可以更深入地了解这个世界，在试图逃离漫漫长夜时，解开谜题并揭开风暴的真正本质。完成游戏并解锁毁灭性的新升级，开启全新的玩法方式。  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/f4f6273fbe7686252283bab62759fed0.poster.avif?t=1724771761\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/f4f6273fbe7686252283bab62759fed0.webm?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/f4f6273fbe7686252283bab62759fed0.mp4?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>&quot;<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>迷人的单人冒险，设定在一个被时间循环困住的世界中。<br> </li><li>射击、躲避、投掷物品和使用超能力，在黑暗之山中战斗。<br> </li><li>所有的升级都是可以无限叠加的，并且可以相互结合，形成混乱的组合。<br> </li><li>装饰旗帜有物理效果。 </li><li>逃脱从一个区域到另一个区域扩散的致命风暴，沿途追赶你登上山顶。<br> </li><li>丰富多彩的可爱角色，他们会在每次游戏中记住你。<br> </li><li>鼓励性奶牛机制？<br> </li><li>发现散落在世界各地的谜题和秘密。<br> </li><li>随机生成的地图，由单独手工制作的房间建成。<br> </li><li>杀手级背景音乐，灵感来自复古芯片音乐，但又带有现代的风格。</li></ul>&quot;  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/75d38ad7a4e09a0f4df3e552d16a9e4b.poster.avif?t=1724771761\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/75d38ad7a4e09a0f4df3e552d16a9e4b.webm?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730080/extras/75d38ad7a4e09a0f4df3e552d16a9e4b.mp4?t=1724771761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
